com.langtoun.oastypes

Interface OASNumberType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OASNumericType, OASType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OASNumberTypeImpl

    public interface OASNumberType
extends OASNumericType
    Public interface for OpenAPI specification number types. Objects of this type are derived from YAML like this: 
    
   type: number
   format: float

   type: number
   format: double
